  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and sauté until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in the minced garlic and cook for another 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add the tomato paste, smoked paprika, cumin, coriander, and cardamom; cook, stirring, for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in the vegetable broth and bring the mixture to a gentle boil.",
    "Add the drained cannellini beans, reduce heat to low, and let the stew simmer for 20 minutes, uncovered, to let the flavors meld.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Finish with a handful of chopped cilantro if using, and serve hot."
  ],
